# Stage 7: Echo Integration

label stage7_integration:
    scene bg garden with fade

    "The Echo agrees to become part of the academy."

    show y at left with dissolve
    show k at right with dissolve

    y "I'll set up the digital framework. Give it a voice, a presence."
    k "And I'll maintain the spiritual anchors. Keep it grounded."

    "The Echo slowly disperses, becoming part of the academy's essence."

    "Echo" "I am... everywhere now. The library's quiet. The garden's peace."
    "Echo" "Not imprisoned. Not free. But... belonging."

    $ mystery_solved = True
    $ ending_type = "integration"

    jump stage7_aftermath
